formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1.	The aforementioned information is certified on the basis of duly signed unaudited books of accounts of the firm as on 31-01-2020 and other information and explanation which to the best of my knowledge and belief were necessary for the purpose of issuing this certificate.
2.	The firm had not maintained separate RERA Account. Therefore, the amount collected from the customers is deposited in bank account mentioned above. Amount deposited and withdrawn from the bank account reflects only booking receipts collected and utilized in the project.
3.	In respect of the all the booked flats on the date of issuing this certificate, the firm is not in possession of Agreement to sale details and in absence of information, I have mentioned the date of sale deed executed instead of date of agreement to sale. Further, I am unable to certify as to whether the firm had entered registered Agreement for Sale with buyers on receipt of consideration in excess of 10% of the apartment value.
4.	I am unable to certify the detail of Mobile No and PAN of the customer, since the necessary evidence is not in the possession of the firm. 
5.	As per guidance note-1 dated 09-07-2019, interest paid on partners capital is not considered in figure of finance cost incurred and paid above.
6.	In respect of the below mentioned flats, the firm is not in possession of the registered agreement of sale, therefore date of agreement to sale is kept blank.
G-4,G-5,F-7,205,404, and 405.
7.	No booking receipts is received from 01-01-2020 to 31-01-2020.
